event_details.name: Hermit's Premature Party

details.shop_desc: Each St. Patrick's Jeweled Chest contains five cards: two are guaranteed to be gear for the four Event Crusaders (at least one of which will be rare or better); two are random trinkets; one is a time warp card. Chests will weight their gear drops towards unfilled slots and upgrades. Gear will only appear for Snickette and Squiggles if you have unlocked those Crusaders.

event_details.description: The Washed-Up Hermit's taking some friends out for St. Patrick's Day a few days ahead of schedule. Who knows what'll happen!

event_details.name: Party Harder

details.shop_desc: Each Party Jeweled Chest contains five cards, of which two are guaranteed to be equipment for Jim the Lumberjack, Kyle the Party Bro, Detective Kaine, Leerion the Royal Dwarf, or Nate Dragon (at least one of which will be rare or better). Also guarantees two random trinkets and one time warp card.
details.promo_chest_desc: Check out these limited-time Party Chests that contain equipment for just the five Crusaders above! (Only for previously unlocked Crusaders)
details.promo_buff_desc: It's time to start wearing buckets on your head and professing your love for vegetables! You just weren't partying hard enough before!
